name: "Faux-Pepe Devil Snake" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description:
[Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] My first tribute to the early days of NFTs and cryptoart! I never knew Pepe in his evil-Nazi flirtation days (I fucking hate racism, so make no mistake about which side of that coin I'm on), but with the renewed interest in early NFT works, I felt it was time to tip my hat to the Primordial Soup!

---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
